CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 7, 1958, pg. A12 reads: "Detroit Smart Set delegation sent Bali Schalk Early, Margaret Piper, Beatrice Mair, and Eva Collins to Pittsburgh for the gala week-end."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four Gay Northeasterner members, from left: Bali Schalk Early, Margaret Piper, Beatrice Mair, and Eva Collins, standing in Penn Sheraton Hotel for grand ball
